Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:12.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried coming alone to our usual park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feeling I've never felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:21.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a child, frightened by the sound of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran back along the path home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:33.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky outside the window is too vast. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, may this reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord, if you ever grant wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:50.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish right now, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:56.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your voice, I miss you! I want to see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you already be looking toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:06.21,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just brush it off, saying the time has slipped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and yet it's been too late since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:19.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give up, it can't be like the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:24.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just decide so simply there's no way, no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.23,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:48.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Joey, Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.51,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.01,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have taken a turn for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That plantlike substance X creature has \Nembedded itself throughout the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's continuing to spread \Nout in all directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The military has put up a defense, \Ntrying to stop its progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think we can rely much on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the well-being of the President \Nat the White House still in question,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a large-scale attack from the \Ngovernment is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we just leave them be, \Nthey'll devour the entire planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.55,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something \Nbefore that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.27,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make the plan to rescue the President,\NOperation Thunderbird, a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.35,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Joey, Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:39.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...says you. So what the \Nhell's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't really know, but we're \Ngoin' after Joey or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it from this girly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I need \Nto talk with Joey about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you tell me to go home, \NI'm not going back, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going for fun and games, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you tell \Nyour parents about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:01.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something to them, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, having another person along might \Ncome in handy during a crisis, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so calm about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Having another person there to pick up Joey \Nafter everything's done would be lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we planning on doing, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:46.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotten the complete support \Nof the government now, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's quite a lot that we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, work will be complete shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon there will be no one \Nleft that can oppose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, no one at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman's power armor that the NIA \Nmade at the Professor's direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The manual said that it amplifies \NHeroman's electrical powers, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this we might make it to the \Nepicenter faster than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A helicopter? Mr. Hughes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:38.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever there's trouble, I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you find Heroman, I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:52.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The All American Network reporter, \NKeisha Jackson, is on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the relay! Is everything set?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Ms. Keisha from the other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:21.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bombers... Are they leaving \Nat your request, Prof. Denton?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But is bombing the Skrugg \Ngoing to accomplish anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not going to bomb anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be using my brain power at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if the only thing I was thinking \Nof doing was attacking the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are they for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For helping Joey and Heroman, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember why Heroman got into a \Njam when he fought that robot, the MR-1?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran out of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then he managed to get through \Nit thanks to that power plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't have to go so well, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this battle is sure to be a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:18.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the power amplification parts \NI designed, his power is not infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:24.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that we'll be in "charge" \Nof Heroman's refueling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to look \Nforward to it when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:39.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for us to accomplish this goal, I've \Ngotten my hands on the best possible equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His heart may be clouded, but Dr. \NMinami is truly a genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Things are gonna get busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:02.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at this! Can \Nyou tell where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what the area surrounding \Nthe White House looks like now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:11.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have ever predicted witnessing \Na transformation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we've just come under \Nattack from the mysterious creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.70,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a helicopter! A \NTV helicopter is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.43,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. You guys \Nconcentrate on the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Who in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up a line to the helicopter in the \Nairspace above the White House, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:24.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's hero, Heroman, is \Nrushing toward the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:27.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to save the President and \Nofficials at this very moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of a broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go back to the studio for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency message from the government...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, they said they'll shoot \Nus down if we don't answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to 'em. Switch over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.76,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.68,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The airspace here is \Nalready a restricted area!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're riskin' our lives \Nout here for this scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but you \Nhave no right to tell us to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.18,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away from the area immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.48,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't we'll shoot you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just consider the pressure you'll face from \Nhaving that exposed on a live national broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:32.12,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman cannot fight freely with you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:37.66,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel any sort of responsibility, \Nplease leave the area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell Heroman he \Nshouldn't worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that would work I wouldn't \Nhave contacted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's his duty to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's our duty to report!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an obligation \Nto report the truth about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already prepared to give \Nour lives for that cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all! Over and out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:16.94,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.74,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Just forget about it up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.28,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that they'll take responsibility \Nfor anything that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.81,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about them, and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I can't do that I \Nasked you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.83,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't seem like they'll budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:39.94,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of wasting time worrying about them, \Nhead to the White House as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.47,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.59,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, now is not the time to be \Nworrying about single individuals...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Saving the entire world is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:17.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman is now breaking through into \Nthe central area of the mysterious creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a shot of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a young boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a young boy right next to Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy is working together with Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is this young boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get that shot over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:05.10,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy is not afraid, \Nand is standing up and fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.69,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.89,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is not a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.33,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,This is reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That boy looks just like Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy... That young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting alongside Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:28.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed to the next phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I even describe this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The body of the mysterious \Ncreature has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... It really is the Skrugg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let what happened to \NCenter City happen again here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:47.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sphere from...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:15.89,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.34,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the US should \Nremember that nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:20.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spheres that put \Nhumanity at its wit's end,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,have begun to move yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The sphere has started to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.40,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,It's floating! It's floating like a balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:40.41,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The sphere that trampled all over \NAmerica is flying in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it's the yummy candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.64,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, can you hear me? Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:54.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've probably noticed this, but \Nsomething has happened to the sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The indestructible sphere \Nwe couldn't analyze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.82,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.20,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,It's floating in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just that one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing is happening with all \Nits friends from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are heading \Nstraight for Washington D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.94,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious the Skrugg \Nare planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry, Joey! You have to \Ndo something before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please rescue the President!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing surprises me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:26.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The NIA's power armor is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnecto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogorr...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skrugg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like you were a bit too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This world will now end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:13.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to resurrect our Lord, Kogorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the Skrugg's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skrugg's true objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:32.40,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get to know you better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:35.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to go at each other with our true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:41.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears and smile are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:46.26,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it is, I won't be scared any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.32,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,With both of us, we can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:54.76,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the one who taught me that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I mutter the words "I was born to meet you"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:07.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,my unease disappears, and my heart burns stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:14.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.30,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:28.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I live feeling the same heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you to the very last,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.68,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the promise built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:40.08,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:45.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We are carving out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. There's only one thing for us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:58.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Heroman, Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:01.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogorr has been resurrected,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's an extremely powerful opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey and Heroman place everything on the line, \Nknowing this battle will decide everyone's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #25: Crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.67,0:24:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
